text: Novokasmartsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Baishevsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 6 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 74 km from Isyangulovo, 9 km from Baishevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Novokasmartsky
